title: Oasis - Definitely Maybe (Guitar tab) PDF
description:
The award-winning debut album by Oasis, that spawned countless imitators and became a catalyst for the 'Cool Britannia' phenomenon that characterised the 1990s. The Oasis sound signified a return to grass-roots rock'n'roll sensibilities with a strong sixties influence. The Gallagher brothers forged anthems filled with a sense of nostalgia and laddish pride, taking the music press by storm with a headline-grabbing swagger.

Every song from the album is transcribed here in accurate Guitar Tab, including the huge hits Live Forever, Supersonic and Cigarettes And Alcohol.
